---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1240px] px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div
      data-reveal
      class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] border border-line bg-gradient-to-br from-[rgba(52,212,184,0.1)] via-surface to-[rgba(91,139,255,0.08)] p-10 sm:p-16 text-center"
    >
      <div class="grain absolute inset-0"></div>
      <div class="relative">
        <h2 class="display text-[clamp(26px,4vw,38px)] text-balance mb-4">
          准备好开始构建了吗？
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-[520px] text-fg-muted text-[16px] text-pretty mb-8">
          注册即可使用 Search 和 Fetch，无需信用卡。从第一个 curl 命令到生产级 Agent，TinyFish 陪你走完全程。
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://agent.tinyfish.ai/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent text-[#04121a] text-[15px] font-semibold px-6 py-3 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(52,212,184,0.32)]"
          >
            免费获取密钥
            <Icon name="arrow" class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://docs.tinyfish.ai/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line bg-surface/60 text-[15px] font-medium px-6 py-3 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-fg-dim"
          >
            阅读文档
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
